GETOPT(3)                 Linux Programmer's Manual                GETOPT(3)
NAME         top

       getopt, getopt_long, getopt_long_only, optarg, optind, opterr, optopt
       - Parse command-line options
SYNOPSIS         top

       #include <unistd.h>

